com.splout.db.qnode.beans
Class DeployInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.splout.db.common.BaseBean
      com.splout.db.qnode.beans.DeployInfo

public class DeployInfo
extends BaseBean

If a deployment is in progress, this bean is serialized as JSON in a file in ZooKeeper so that any QNode can know that there is a deploy in progress and at what time it started, etc. This bean is also returned for the deploy() method in QNode.
